rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard you crushed the anti-Empire
organization, Lindwurm! As expected
of you...!

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Hearing that Don and Bahn were captured,
it seems Senator Stole has finally
started to confess.

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It's strange for me to say this, but...
thank you.

rows.label: tlk41310151_04_msg0004
rows.name:
The Empire being protected means
I won't lose my job, and I can
provide for my brothers!
